name: Arena 51
description: Well, simply put, this is an arena for the classics! This is not a Shotgun2 though, you will find weapons and powerups placed intelligently. If you have been a deathmatch nut for quite a while, you will see that this level can function as Shotgun2, DWANGO7 map 5(?) "Arena", and DWANGO6 map 8 - all in one!!
